  "title": "Clinic Assistant / Patient Care Assistant (Clinic) #79037",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Medical Clinic / General Practitioner</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Clinic Assistant / Patient Care Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Sengkang West Avenue</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT Pay + Medical Benefits</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Register patients and manage dispensing of medications, including stock checks.</li><li>Prepare for blood tests, complete required forms, and process X-ray request forms.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of the clinic and ensure accurate record keeping.</li><li>Handle GP insurance and CHAS claims.</li><li>Answer phone calls and respond to patient queries via WhatsApp.</li><li>Schedule and manage patient appointments.</li><li>Assist the doctor with procedures, wound dressing, and other treatments.</li><li>Perform autoclaving for instruments.</li><li>Prepare and pack medications for dispensing.</li><li>Provide administrative support and assist with any other ad hoc duties as required.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE 'O' Level or relevant certificate in healthcare support or administration.</li><li>Able to multitask, work in a fast-paced environment, and handle patients with empathy and</li><li>professionalism.</li><li>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office and clinic management systems preferred.</li><li>Some relevant experience would be advantageous.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79037 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
